Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.83,0:00:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學 怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.48,0:00:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒甚麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.88,0:00:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請走這邊 祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.19,0:00:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.92,0:00:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳 這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.87,0:00:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉安女學園 山百合版灰姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.40,0:00:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經用螢光筆作上了記號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉紅色的是灰姑娘 藍色的是姐姐B
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐B？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.89,0:00:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是灰姑娘的壞心眼姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.56,0:00:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你不演灰姑娘時 希望你能演這個角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.23,0:00:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.77,0:00:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你為甚麼會在這種地方吃午飯呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.85,0:00:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學正在逃避新聞部的采訪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.52,0:01:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 我們學校的新聞部采訪的方法很強硬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.34,0:01:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳 接受念珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.48,0:01:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就可以替你回答那些采訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.29,0:01:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意的話 可以隨時來找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.03,0:01:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.04,0:01:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還本想讓她同意在校慶時展示照片呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.50,0:01:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 祥子大人討厭櫻花與銀杏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.05,0:01:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.82,0:01:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才讓人吃驚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.98,0:01:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她竟然能堅持著到這裡來找祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在瑪莉亞的庭院裡的少女們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.90,0:01:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也帶著天使般無垢的笑容 穿越與身同高的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.28,0:02:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆蓋住純潔身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.88,0:02:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓裙子的摺痕亂掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.76,0:02:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓白色的水手服領結外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒緩地行走成了這裡的習俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立莉莉安女學園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是少女的花園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.28,0:03:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}月與念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請教一個問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.12,0:04:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難的問題可別找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.98,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼白薔薇大人會選志摩子同學做妹妹呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很困難不過倒是很少見的問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於選擇志摩子的原因一般不會有誰問到呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.19,0:04:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是因為志摩子同學\n看起來就像是應該被選中的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我完全相反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.01,0:04:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得這麼軟弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我是稻秸嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.55,0:04:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白薔薇大人說的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.70,0:04:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對祥子大人來說 我是迎頭撞上並被抓住的稻秸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.75,0:04:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這樣說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還真佩服自己能比喻得這麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻秸 不是很好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一點好呀？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.19,0:04:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被祥子一直握在手裡這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像志摩子這種人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.57,0:05:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得就該讓她為山百合會好好發揮其才能嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.02,0:05:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是剛才的問題的答案吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.57,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以白薔薇的身份回答的話 這個就是答案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.13,0:05:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 以個人來說到還有其它的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.76,0:05:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.57,0:05:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否反倒是志摩子在羡慕著祐巳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 為甚麼會突然跳到那種話上啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.90,0:05:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看祐巳那可愛而又變化豐富的表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.47,0:05:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等… 白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然「長者」來了就到此結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.91,0:05:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長者？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好像很開心嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.65,0:05:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦 就是看見祥子進來才服務一下的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.85,0:05:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.57,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 不快點洗杯子的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是大家快到這裡的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳真是一個好孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓祥子嫉妒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我也該去看看樓下的情形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.43,0:06:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會穿上紅色的天鵝絨禮服去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.94,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我穿著平常的裙子就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.20,0:06:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要在有金色花卉圖案的披風上別上鑽石別針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.28,0:06:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 頭髮像這樣如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.24,0:06:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙杜瑞拉 你跟我們一起去舞會不是挺好的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.54,0:06:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是記得很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.70,0:07:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被白薔薇大人撫摸頭或擁抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也從未有過這麼強烈的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 剛才去取劇裝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 好像真的是正在忙碌中呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在做劇本的練習而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要試穿服裝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天是試穿服裝與排練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.31,0:07:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以花寺的學生會長也會過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經清楚地轉告過了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.29,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子也需要參加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也該是去迎接的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.46,0:07:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳 你能去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.61,0:07:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏木同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也就是花寺的學生會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.70,0:07:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該在正門那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.22,0:07:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能跑 不能跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還會踩到銀杏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.48,0:07:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 失禮了 請問是柏木同學嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山百合會的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是柏木優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.12,0:08:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天請多多關照了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.15,0:08:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經確定能進入花寺的大學了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.37,0:08:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是附屬中學 若非成績優秀是不可能不參加考試就合格吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.20,0:08:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 能否在這裡稍等片刻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去換一下拖鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是讓人無法挑剔的王子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻被灰姑娘所討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我看錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.82,0:08:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人應該在薔薇館裡才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝各位的款待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常漂亮的公館啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人不在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.34,0:08:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.62,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花寺的學生會長 客觀地來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.99,0:09:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.27,0:09:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客觀來看 相當的不錯啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說作為祥子的對手沒甚麼不足的地方了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.33,0:09:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.24,0:09:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的戲劇其實還有另一個目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.61,0:09:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是克服祥子的厭男症
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.23,0:09:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子的家庭相當地複雜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.46,0:09:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖父與父親都在外面偷藏了女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.67,0:09:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人會討厭男人原來也是事出有由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 灰姑娘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了句「我先去體育館」就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.65,0:09:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我也先去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看見的果然是祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.47,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說已經回去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.84,0:09:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.65,0:10:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.46,0:10:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.39,0:10:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在圖書館旁邊的路上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.08,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒去過那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙子會被弄髒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.61,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼祥子大人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.59,0:10:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才剛注意到這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.76,0:10:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.14,0:10:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實去過那個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早點看看對方的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.82,0:10:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.99,0:11:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想比對方更早地看到 就只有這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.42,0:11:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.53,0:11:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與花寺的學生會長跳舞的確非我本意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.17,0:11:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但逃避就意味著認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起其它任何東西 我最討厭的就是認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.48,0:11:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家到來之前 讓我來做你的舞伴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.91,0:11:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用了 不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.08,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.78,0:11:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是記住了舞步 但還無法跳得很流暢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算您這樣說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.68,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用想太多 信任自已身體的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別急躁 面帶微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.19,0:11:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.58,0:11:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.97,0:11:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.42,0:11:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.82,0:11:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.18,0:11:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.27,0:11:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 舞姿慢慢變得漂亮起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.39,0:11:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞原來是一件這麼愉快的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.87,0:11:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 我以前也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.04,0:12:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我叫小笠原 請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.09,0:12:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請你多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.26,0:12:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帥氣吧 柏木同學的王子裝扮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你們也換裝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.49,0:12:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.89,0:12:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.23,0:12:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口好像太松了一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要稍微提供一點服務嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.82,0:12:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是甚麼服務啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.43,0:12:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你最美麗的裝扮做為禮物送給FAN們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.18,0:12:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣最合適吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.73,0:12:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會是你來穿哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對祐巳來說好像稍微大了點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許改小一點會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.96,0:12:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.28,0:13:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會演灰姑娘現在還沒決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.54,0:13:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 交換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.89,0:13:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～ 祐巳也好可愛 好可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.79,0:13:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.60,0:13:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 對我來說胸口實在是太鬆了一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.82,0:13:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.36,0:13:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.75,0:13:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.42,0:13:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.96,0:13:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.47,0:13:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.16,0:13:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.72,0:13:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.28,0:13:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.44,0:13:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.99,0:13:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.59,0:13:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.22,0:13:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.54,0:13:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.22,0:13:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.30,0:13:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.91,0:13:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.52,0:13:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.95,0:13:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.63,0:13:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.13,0:13:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2 2 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 休息15分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.05,0:13:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子 我知道你不喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過能否稍微讓大家看見一點笑容？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.22,0:13:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那樣會影響到觀眾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式上場時我會好好地笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.89,0:14:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 如果有我能幫上忙的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.30,0:14:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就接受我的念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.64,0:14:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.40,0:14:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說有想拜托祐巳的事 就只有這件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真那麼討厭嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.44,0:14:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常討厭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.25,0:14:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話想對你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳 你先回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.79,0:14:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.61,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 柏木同學說有話要對她講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.99,0:14:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位主角都不在 也排練不起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.55,0:14:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 稍等一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想就這樣放棄排練嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子不是那樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.79,0:14:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.26,0:14:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我 我也去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.57,0:15:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分頭去找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.73,0:15:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.23,0:15:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白薔薇大人 這種時候了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.34,0:15:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡祥子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.19,0:15:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.87,0:15:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅薔薇大人與黃薔薇大人以及令也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概志摩子與由乃也是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.46,0:15:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使看起來很乾練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.73,0:15:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也衹不過是高中生 所以難免會膽怯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕去知道發生了甚麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有不該去找出真相的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.71,0:15:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去找祥子大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是討厭的銀杏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.52,0:15:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.85,0:15:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.46,0:15:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為那傢伙絕對不會對祥子出手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.82,0:15:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為同類所以知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹甚麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開你的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.72,0:16:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子 不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳 去叫守衛來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.72,0:16:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為會讓祥子大人感到為難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.23,0:16:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼你會這麼想？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.18,0:16:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為您臉上這樣寫著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.19,0:16:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚擾到大家真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才只是有點小的爭吵而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.40,0:16:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你一定要向大家說明情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.96,0:16:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.86,0:16:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柏木優是我的表兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.30,0:16:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只如此 他還是我的未婚夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未…婚！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.29,0:16:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們即使不作戲也能互擁雙肩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是接吻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意忘形了嗎 還不停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.12,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.31,0:17:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.81,0:17:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我也不知該怎樣才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚麼也幫不上祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.83,0:17:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是叫大家來這裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.13,0:17:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.73,0:18:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.48,0:18:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人 請給我念珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.14,0:18:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.42,0:18:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.98,0:18:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.60,0:18:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我改變主意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.44,0:18:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優…他並不喜歡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.68,0:18:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因為我是獨生女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.23,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他有帶領小笠原集團的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙親都希望我們兩人結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他才會說要和我結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.02,0:18:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.88,0:18:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡柏木同學吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.69,0:18:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自已喜歡的人並非因為喜歡自已而要與自已結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.21,0:18:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你聽我訴說這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.33,0:18:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也包括我的懺悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.18,0:18:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒法向任何人訴說 所以一直很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經不要緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.22,0:19:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 祥子大人 請給我念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.65,0:19:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再逃避了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.48,0:19:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個溫室裡半數以上的植物都是薔薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.51,0:19:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是紅薔薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四季常開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.32,0:19:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好記住這種花吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.03,0:19:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.98,0:19:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.50,0:19:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人已回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.57,0:19:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請擦乾凈拖鞋的底面再進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.72,0:19:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可把銀杏的臭味帶入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.34,0:20:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不會再去薔薇館了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.15,0:20:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會再和祥子大人講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.74,0:20:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀演出成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.38,0:20:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演得太好了 祥子大人的灰姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.27,0:20:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發現了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.33,0:20:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.06,0:20:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在跳舞時踩了優的腳三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.95,0:20:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我能笑出來都是托祐巳的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚麼也沒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.86,0:20:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能稍微陪我一會兒嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.39,0:20:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 能掛在祐巳的頸上嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.09,0:21:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既非打賭 也非同情甚麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.44,0:21:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是神聖的儀式
